    "ops.load(1, 1000000.0, 0, 1000000.0)\n",

   "source": [
    "ops.wipeAnalysis()\n",
    "ops.constraints(\"Transformation\")\n",
    "ops.system(\"BandGeneral\")\n",
    "ops.numberer(\"Plain\")\n",

    "ops.algorithm(\"Newton\")\n",
    "ops.integrator(\"Newmark\", 0.5, 0.25)\n",
    "ops.analysis(\"Transient\")"
